List of USGS parameter codes

Source: R/tabbedDataRetrievals.R
parameterCdFile.Rd

Complete list of USGS parameter codes as of May 22, 2017.

Value

parameterData data frame with information about USGS parameters.

NameTypeDescription
parameter_cdcharacter5-digit USGS parameter code
parameter_group_nmcharacterUSGS parameter group name
parameter_nmcharacterUSGS parameter name
casrncharacterChemical Abstracts Service (CAS) Registry Number
srsnamecharacterSubstance Registry Services Name
parameter_unitscharacterParameter units

Examples

head(parameterCdFile[,1:2])
#>   parameter_cd parameter_group_nm
#> 1        00001        Information
#> 2        00002        Information
#> 3        00003        Information
#> 4        00005        Information
#> 5        00008        Information
#> 6        00009        Information
